==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Truster
<hw>Trust"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
trusts, or credits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>One who makes a trust; -- the
correlative of <xex>trustee</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trustful</ent>⟦br⟧
